reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great item for price
reviews.reviewText: The chair is smaller than I thought, but perfect for our space. Easy to assemble, comfortable for short periods of time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. It is my first time owning a office chair but I love it so much! It took an hour to build and I’m very happy with it!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: this arrived in two boxes, the second interior box looked like a return, there were missing pieces and no instructions. despite that, it was easy to assemble, need a "star" Allen wrench, not sure of the size, price was good, considering other retailers and shipping costs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: For those of you who said parts are missing. Please look inside of the back of the back rest of the chair. I thought I was gonna cry when my chair arrived and I didn’t see the parts to assemble nor did I see the manual. Just before I started to boo hoo out of sheer frustration, I happened to unzip the back rest and VOILA! There everything was…and when I saw the manual..it actually read that parts in the back of the chair! I love my new chair. Very very comfortable and easy to assemble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024

reviews.reviewText: I have recieved this item/chair twice now. I got my box and it was missing the arm rests and the wheel stand. I returned the item and got a replacement today.
